 Warden on <a href=HTTP://forums.ayonae.ro target=akztarg>Ayonae Ro</a>-- Proud Member of <a href=HTTP://www.fellowshipofdragons.com target=akztarg>Fellowship of Dragons</a><br><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=688542 target=akztarg>Lidium - Myrmidon of 58 seasons on Ayonae Ro</a><br><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=701495 target=akztarg>Miegromper - 41st season Pally on Ayonae Ro</a></td></tr>
